                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-862" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MANLEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, F</hi> 148.) I saw the prisoner running away—I stopped him—the prosecutor came up and gave him into custody, and gave me this handkerchief.</p>
